{
  "id": "gen-hyper-rainbow-vortex",
  "name": "Hyper Rainbow Vortex",
  "category": "generative",
  "url": "shaders/gen-hyper-rainbow-vortex.wgsl",
  "description": "A multi-layered chromatic vortex enriched with Wolfram Rankine fluid dynamics: solid-body rotation inside a bass-reactive core and irrotational flow outside. Angular velocity modulated by mids. Mouse spawns secondary vortices. Full upgraded-rgba stack with ACES tone mapping, temporal feedback, chromatic aberration, and semantic alpha.",
